.TH AGENT-HOOK-POST-MCP 1 "2026-06-30" "agentguard" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
agent-hook-post-mcp \- track MCP tool failure streaks
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B agent-hook-post-mcp
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B agent-hook-post-mcp
reads an MCP hook JSON payload from standard input and records success or
failure for the target MCP server. The pre-MCP hook uses those counters as a
circuit breaker after repeated failures.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Failure tracking completed.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR agent-hook-pre-mcp (1)
